example1.atlassian.net being the target instance you're trying to create the one-way link _to_.

It would be a great improvement if the logs would tell us if anything went wrong on a migration to OnDemand. For instance, the groups that were granted the *JIRA Users* global permission were not migrated correctly and the association between the permission and the groups had to be set up manually. Our current logs don't log any information about it, which makes it really hard to troubleshoot these cases:

